questions.explanation:
&lt;p&gt;The logic applied in this question is&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(First number x second number) -&amp;nbsp;second number = Third number&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Revannath_Teaching_2.11.2022_D9.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 48px; width: 216px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;(5 * 30) - 30= 150 - 30 = 120&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now in 2nd row apply the same logic&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Revannath_Teaching_2.11.2022_D10.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 77px; width: 246px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(7 x 56) - 56 =&amp;nbsp; 392 - 56 = 336&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Now in 3rd row apply the same logic&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Revannath_Teaching_2.11.2022_D11.png&quot; style=&quot;height: 62px; width: 246px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(9 x 90) - 90 = 810 - 90 = 720&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;the correct answer is 720&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&gt;इस प्रश्न में लागू तर्क इस प्रकार&amp;nbsp;है&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(पहली संख्या x दूसरी संख्या) - दूसरी संख्या = तीसरी संख्या&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Revannath_Teaching_2.11.2022_D9.png&quot; style=&quot; height: 48px; width: 216px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(5 * 30) - 30= 150 - 30 = 120&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;अब दूसरी पंक्ति में समान&amp;nbsp;तर्क लागू कीजिये&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Revannath_Teaching_2.11.2022_D10.png&quot; style=&quot; height: 77px; width: 246px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(7 x 56) - 56 =&amp;nbsp; 392 - 56 = 336&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;अब तीसरी पंक्ति में&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;समान&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;तर्क लागू कीजिये&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;//storage.googleapis.com/tb-img/production/22/11/F1_Revannath_Teaching_2.11.2022_D11.png&quot; style=&quot; height: 62px; width: 246px;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(9 x 90) - 90 = 810 - 90 = 720&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;अत:, &lt;strong&gt;सही उत्तर 720 है।&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

